Name: ClickCells:  Winter Lady
About the game: Erotic casual puzzle! The player's goal to keep the blue block on the platform for 3 seconds in order to pass the level. As a reward you get pictures of a beautiful girl! This game has images of a naked girl. The game is for people over 18 years old! Also by numerous requests in the game appeared 'administrator mode'. Administrator mode Press the F button while at the art or puzzle level and you will immediately open the entire block of five puzzles and get the corresponding achievements. There's a game waiting for you Interesting puzzles Art from LeArtNi Nice music from Trauerbaum Beautiful achievements Powered by Clickteam Fusion 2.5
